nodes.text: A vendor sold vinefish near Yinta Lake on the planet of Vulta. The vendor attempted to sell some the freshly grilled vinefish to smuggler Zeerid Korr in the year 3653 BBY. Korr was on his way to meet with his daughter, Arra Yooms, when the vendor called out to Korr. Korr did not buy any of the vinefish, however, and continued on his way.
The vendor first appeared in the novel The Old Republic: Deceived, written by Paul S. Kemp and published on March 22, 2011.
